Package de.uniheidelberg.cl.swp.io Description

Classes for input and output related tasks.
ACRResultWriter writes the results of the ACR-Systems to a file.
Configuration interface to the config.xml file.
Logging logs important information in the training and testing process.
MMAXFileFilter filters MMAX files.
